snippet: Michael Vick overcame four interceptions, rallying the penalty-prone Philadelphia Eagles to a nerve-racking 17-16 win over the Cleveland Browns.
abstract: NFL Roundup; Philadelphia Eagles quarterback Michael Vick overcomes four interceptions to beat the Cleveland Browns, 17-16, in season opener; other results noted.
lead_paragraph: Michael Vick overcame four interceptions, rallying the penalty-prone Philadelphia Eagles to a nerve-racking 17-16 win over the Cleveland Browns.

headline.main: Vick Shakes Off Rust, and Then Shakes Off Browns
